short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: usansible ... support your Ansible Development. this tool provides you with two functions.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
1. Ansible Document Search

type "usa" in Chrome address-bar and input keyword(e.g. "dnf"), you can access directly "Search Result" in Ansible Documentation Website.

2. Access to Collections(Module/Plugin) source file in GitHub

add a link to GitHub on Collections documentation page.
